## 3.3 Email Generation (AI)

### Pre-Generation Input Flow

Before generating email, prompt user for:

```
{
  purpose: string (e.g. sales, outreach, follow-up)
  tone: formal | casual | persuasive
  productDetails: string
  CTA: string
  additionalInstructions?: string
}
```

### AI Generation

* Generate:

  * Subject
  * Body (MDX / rich text)
* Include placeholders:

  * {{firstName}}
  * {{lastName}}
  * {{company}}
  * Custom fields

---

## 3.4 Personalization Engine

### Modes

#### 1. Manual Personalization

User inputs per-contact:

```
personalizationNotes
customFields
```

#### 2. AI Research-Based Personalization

User provides:

```
researchPrompt: string
```

System performs:

* Fetch company/contact info (via APIs or scraping layer)
* Generate insights:

  * Recent news
  * Role-based context
  * Company summary

AI generates:

```
personalizedSnippet(contact)
```

Inserted into email:

```
{{personalizedIntro}}
```

---

