## 3.6 Bulk Email Sending

### Flow

1. Select Contact List
2. Select Template
3. Preview emails (sample + per contact)
4. Send

### Processing Logic

For each contact:

```
email.body = replacePlaceholders(template.body, contact)
email.body += personalizedSnippet(contact)
sendEmail(email)
logResult()
```

### Features

* Rate limiting
* Retry on failure
* Email provider integration (SMTP / APIs)

