## 4. Placeholder System

### Supported Placeholders

```
{{firstName}}
{{lastName}}
{{email}}
{{company}}
{{custom.<fieldName>}}
{{personalizedIntro}}
```

### Engine

```
function replacePlaceholders(template, contact) {
  // Replace standard fields
  // Replace custom fields
  // Inject personalization snippet
}
```

